---
// Contact component for FluxCore Systems
---

<section id="advantages" class="py-20 bg-slate-950 relative overflow-hidden" data-ps="src/components/home/Contact.astro:contact">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 reveal" data-ps="src/components/home/Contact.astro:1ijz28">
    <div class="text-center mb-16" data-ps="src/components/home/Contact.astro:o1wuzb">
      <div class="inline-block w-12 h-1 bg-[#E85D1A] mb-8" data-ps="src/components/home/Contact.astro:1ijz29"></div>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black text-white mb-4 tracking-tighter leading-tight" data-ps="src/components/home/Contact.astro:fguuu1">Our Advantages</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-[#E85D1A] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest" data-ps="src/components/home/Contact.astro:crxs8w">
        Why Customers Choose Elsan
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8" data-ps="src/components/home/Contact.astro:1ijz2a">
      <!-- Advantage 1 -->
      <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-8 border border-slate-800 hover:border-[#E85D1A]/50 transition-colors group" data-ps="src/components/home/Contact.astro:o1wuza">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#E85D1A]/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-[#E85D1A] transition-colors" data-ps="src/components/home/Contact.astro:o1wuz9">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6 text-[#E85D1A] group-hover:text-white" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4" data-ps="src/components/home/Contact.astro:30swuz">Turkish Engineering. Nigerian Market.</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/components/home/Contact.astro:u4l0au">Elsan Transformer brings the quality and precision of Turkish transformer manufacturing — trusted and exported to over 100 countries globally — directly to the Nigerian and West African power market. Internationally certified, locally supported</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Advantage 2 -->
      <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-8 border border-slate-800 hover:border-[#E85D1A]/50 transition-colors group" data-ps="src/components/home/Contact.astro:1ijz25">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#E85D1A]/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-[#E85D1A] transition-colors" data-ps="src/components/home/Contact.astro:1ijz26">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6 text-[#E85D1A] group-hover:text-white" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4" data-ps="src/components/home/Contact.astro:30swv0">One of West Africa's Broadest Transformer Ranges</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/components/home/Contact.astro:u4l0av">With distribution transformers from 25 kVA to 2,500 kVA and power transformers from 3.15 MVA to 50 MVA, Elsan offers one of the most comprehensive transformer manufacturing ranges available in Nigeria and the West African market.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Advantage 3 -->
      <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-8 border border-slate-800 hover:border-[#E85D1A]/50 transition-colors group" data-ps="src/components/home/Contact.astro:1ijz27">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#E85D1A]/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-[#E85D1A] transition-colors" data-ps="src/components/home/Contact.astro:1ijz28">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6 text-[#E85D1A] group-hover:text-white" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16z"/><polyline points="3.29 7 12 12 20.71 7"/><line x1="12" y1="22" x2="12" y2="12"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4" data-ps="src/components/home/Contact.astro:30swv1">IEC 60076 & ISO 9001 Certified</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/components/home/Contact.astro:u4l0aw">Full compliance with IEC 60076 and ISO 9001:2015 for guaranteed reliability. Every unit undergoes complete routine testing before dispatch — no exceptions</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Advantage 4 -->
      <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-8 border border-slate-800 hover:border-[#E85D1A]/50 transition-colors group" data-ps="src/components/home/Contact.astro:1ijz2b">
      <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#E85D1A]/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-[#E85D1A] transition-colors" data-ps="src/components/home/Contact.astro:1ijz2c">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6 text-[#E85D1A] group-hover:text-white" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2v4"/><path d="m16.2 7.8 2.9-2.9"/><path d="M18 12h4"/><path d="m16.2 16.2 2.9 2.9"/><path d="M12 18v4"/><path d="m4.9 19.1 2.9-2.9"/><path d="M2 12h4"/><path d="m4.9 4.9 2.9 2.9"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4" data-ps="src/components/home/Contact.astro:30swv2">Uncompromising Quality</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/components/home/Contact.astro:u4l0ax">Every transformer is built using premium materials, precision-engineered components, and tested rigorously before delivery to ensure it performs reliably from day one in any Nigerian grid or industrial environment.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Advantage 5 -->
      <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-8 border border-slate-800 hover:border-[#E85D1A]/50 transition-colors group" data-ps="src/components/home/Contact.astro:1ijz2b">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#E85D1A]/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-[#E85D1A] transition-colors" data-ps="src/components/home/Contact.astro:1ijz2c">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6 text-[#E85D1A] group-hover:text-white" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4" data-ps="src/components/home/Contact.astro:30swv3">Technical Support & After-Sales</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/components/home/Contact.astro:u4l0ay">Our engineering team assists with specifications, installation guidance, commissioning support, and spare parts throughout the full lifetime of your equipment across Nigeria and West Africa.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Advantage 6 -->
      <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-8 border border-slate-800 hover:border-[#E85D1A]/50 transition-colors group" data-ps="src/components/home/Contact.astro:1ijz2d">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#E85D1A]/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-[#E85D1A] transition-colors" data-ps="src/components/home/Contact.astro:1ijz2e">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6 text-[#E85D1A] group-hover:text-white" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4" data-ps="src/components/home/Contact.astro:30swv4">Custom Solutions</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/components/home/Contact.astro:u4l0bk">We design and manufacture transformers to specific voltage ratios, tap ranges, cooling classes, and installation requirements — ideal for non-standard or complex applications including solar PV and off-grid projects</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Background Decoration -->
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-[#E85D1A]/50 to-transparent" data-ps="src/components/home/Contact.astro:1ijz2e"></div>
</section>
